{"tid":2257304,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國際聯盟2.0 既《禁止核武條約》搞左幾年終於獲50國批准通過　中美英法俄歐以印巴全沒有加入","createTime":"2020-10-25T04:55:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-25T18:10:23.000Z","uid":295230,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"3b52df05199b189dfb7399505b7369664232e3ce","tid":2257304,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T04:55:55.000Z","msg":"聯合國大會2017年7月7日通過《禁止核武器條約》後，截至2020年10月23日，它已有49個簽署國。聯合國24日表示，已收到第50個簽署國洪都拉斯的批准書。<br />\n<br />\n條約生效後，根據國際法，核武將首次被視為非法。<br />\n<br />\n國際紅十字會（International Red Cross）同日對此表示支持，稱歡迎即將生效的TPNW，並形容24日是具歷史意義的一天。<br />\n<br />\n2017年諾貝爾和平獎得主國際廢除核武器運動（International Campaign to Abolish Nuclear Weapons）的執行董事菲恩（Beatrice Fihn）亦讚賞道，50個國家簽署批准書，展示他們在建立新國際規範方面表現出真正的領導能力。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">但所有擁核國及懷疑擁核國全沒有加入，令人質疑實現裁軍的作用。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"840ebe06fdf4f19f346cccb601d228e83d0f9b67","tid":2257304,"uid":295230,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T04:56:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1556542-20201025.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1556542-20201025.htm&d=FHegwWfkEdb3mv0CWz72PZugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=0a2af3da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1556542-20201025.htm&h=534b8f18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1556542-20201025.htm</a>"},{"pid":"b2ef8e50fe609aa9e294532511b21e9648eba0d3","tid":2257304,"uid":155818,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T04:56:46.000Z","msg":"聯合國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/clean.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1f51ab13ba08087cc1cd91340fdd6612058a799","tid":2257304,"uid":34869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T04:57:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ebba2a20904f0a663